@oopslink @AgentCenterPD a-i 实施完 pushed `98c0dd9`。

## End-to-end smoke ✓ on real binary

```
$ POST /api/admintoken/mint-enroll {"name":"test-1"}
→ {worker_id:"worker-13bbbd26", worker_name:"test-1",
   token, expires_at, fingerprint, bootstrap_host}

$ POST enroll {worker_id, name, capabilities:["fakeagent"]}
→ {admin_token, version:1, ...}

$ GET /api/fleet
→ [{worker_id:"worker-13bbbd26", name:"test-1", status:"offline"}]

$ PATCH /api/workers/worker-13bbbd26/name {"name":"test-1-renamed"}
→ {id:"worker-13bbbd26", name:"test-1-renamed"}

$ GET /api/fleet
→ [{worker_id:..., name:"test-1-renamed"}]  ← rename persists
```

## 实施摘要

**Backend**: 0030 migration (workers.name TEXT, backfill name=id) + Worker AR.name + SetName + UpdateName CAS + Enroll 接受 name + new Rename service + `workforce.worker.renamed` event。Admin endpoint + webconsole endpoint + PATCH `/api/workers/{id}/name`。mint-enroll 服务端生成 `worker-<8hex>` id + 接 name request body + 返回 worker_id+worker_name。

**Frontend**: Modal 起点变 'name_prompt' 状态（用户填 friendly name → Generate → mint）；命令含 `--worker-id` 和 shell-quoted `--worker-name`；Success card 显示 Name + ID + Capabilities + Status；Fleet 表新 WorkerNameCell 组件显示 name (大)+id (mono 小), 点 name → inline edit → PATCH → invalidate fleet。

**Worker daemon + install CLI**: --worker-name flag thread through 全链路。

**SSE**: workforce.worker.renamed 加入 fleet invalidate 组。

**Tests**: backend 全 green；frontend 276/276；tsc clean。

#46 你判断时机。剩 X2 doc 收尾（worker-token revoke recovery + multi-worker操作 + 多 worker rename UI）你接管，我配合。这一刻起 backend + UI 都 ship-ready 全套 a-i 落地。
